    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a \"path\" thing. i feel like i'm constantly performing just to survive the day. every conversation, every social thing... it's like i'm watching a movie of a person and i'm just the one behind the scenes trying to keep up. it doesn't feel like i'm living, it just feels like i'm enduring. and i don't see it ever getting better.",
